            "text": "Finished in Shadow Gray Metallic over a red interior, this new 'Vette looks just as good as it is powerful. Exterior-wise, the Z51 package includes a front splitter and rear spoiler to help with aerodynamics. Carbon Flash painted aluminum wheels with a machined lip (19-inch front, 20-inch rear) are wrapped with high-performance run-flat rubber. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
